metadata.name: Lunch Date
metadata.description:
It's lunchtime. 🍗

Both Noki and Aino are on their break. They've decided to get some lunch together. Noki can't seem to decide what she wants to eat. Aino doesn't really care about the food as long as Noki's there. 😊💖

They've been walking around the town for hours, looking for good food and enjoying each other company. It's most likely past their break time already. 😱⌚

I wonder what they end up getting for lunch (or dinner)?

---
